text: Enamul Haq Manju () is a Bangladesh Jamaat-e-Islami politician and the former Member of Parliament of Cox's Bazar-1. ==Career== Manju was elected to parliament from Cox's Bazar-1 as a Bangladesh Jamaat-e-Islami candidate in 1991. ==References== Category:Bangladesh Jamaat-e-Islami politicians Category:Living people Category:5th Jatiya Sangsad members Category:People from Cox's Bazar District Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
